Tzipora Desmoisnes # Introduction # Tzipora Desmoisnes (also Zelda lo Ula Desmoisnes, born May 5 2047) is a Vekllei Gregori Baby and librarian, and is the character utopia of the [Petticoat Project]. Born to artist and political activist Mette Sumoisnesn and an unknown father, the family moved to Colombia when Tzipora was six months old.
